title: Inpsect and try to interpret your scikit-learn machine-learning models
description:
Speaker:: Guillaume Lemaitre

Track: PyData: Machine Learning & Stats
This tutorial presents the different inspection techniques currently available to inspect a machine-learning model developed with scikit-learn. In addition, we compare all these methods and pinpoint their limitations.


Recorded at the PyConDE & PyData Berlin 2022 conference, April 11-13 2022.
